Kun lataat tiedostoja internetistä, Download Status Bar lisää automaattisesti tiedostot latauspalkkiin. Kuten nimikin jo kertoo, latauspalkki on palkki jonka Firefox luo yleensä lisäosapalkin yläpuolelle. Koska Download Status Bar on käyttäjäystävällinen ja viisas, latauspalkki on näkyvillä vain kun sinulla on aktiivisia latauksia. Jos näytettäviä latauksia ei ole, latauspalkki piilottaa itsensä automaattisesti.

Jos haluat näyttää latauspalkin, voit painaa seuraavia näppäimiä:

&lt;b&gt;Windows: CTRL + ALT + D&lt;/b&gt;

&lt;b&gt;Mac OS X: SHIFT + ALT + D&lt;/b&gt;

&lt;b&gt;Linux (CTRL/CMD) + ALT + D&lt;/b&gt;

Voit myös käyttää ylläolevia näppäimiä piilottaaksesi latauspalkin milloin haluat. As another option, you can toggle Download Bar by Download Status Bar menu option under Tools menu of Firefox.

Kun avaat latauspalkin, näet Lataukset-napin vasemmalla ja Tyhjennä-napin palkin oikealla puolella. Lataukset-napista saat esiin valikon. Tyhjennä-nappi tyhjentää kaikki valmiit lataukset latauspalkista.

Kun painat Lataukset-nappia, saat esiin valikon kuten kerrottu alla.:
&lt;ul&gt;&lt;li&gt;&lt;b&gt;Asetukset:&lt;/b&gt; Tämä valinta avaa asetukset josta voit mukauttaa lisäosaa tarpeidesi mukaan.&lt;/li&gt;&lt;li&gt;&lt;b&gt;Tilastot:&lt;/b&gt; Tämä valinta avaa tilastot josta näet tilastoja perustuen latauksiisi.&lt;/li&gt;&lt;li&gt;&lt;b&gt;Näytä lataushistoria:&lt;/b&gt; Tämä valinta näyttää Firefoxin täydellisen lataushistorian.&lt;/li&gt;&lt;li&gt;&lt;b&gt;Avaa Lataukset-välilehti:&lt;/b&gt; Tämä valinta avaa Firefoxin lataushistorian välilehteen.&lt;/li&gt;&lt;li&gt;&lt;b&gt;Lataukset:&lt;/b&gt; Tämä valinta antaa sinun hallita kaikkien latauksiesi tilaa kerralla.&lt;/li&gt;&lt;li&gt;&lt;b&gt;Apua:&lt;/b&gt; Tämä valinta avaa Download Status Barin apusivun josta saat tietoa lisäosasta ja siitä, kuinka käyttää sitä hyödyllisellä tavalla.&lt;/li&gt;&lt;li&gt;&lt;b&gt;Sulje palkki:&lt;/b&gt; Tämä valinta sulkee latauspalkin.&lt;/li&gt;&lt;/ul&gt;When you download files from web, Download Status Bar automatically places download items in Download Bar. Below are some example software from Mozilla to download. Click on them to start downloading.

&lt;a rel="nofollow" href="http://outgoing.mozilla.org/v1/6c67e8b626205e8d96b2d0baae45371c6e78c868557026da755005d4e8e7a252/https%3A//download.mozilla.org/%3Fproduct=firefox-26.0&amp;amp;os=osx&amp;amp;lang=en-US"&gt;Firefox&lt;/a&gt;

&lt;a rel="nofollow" href="http://outgoing.mozilla.org/v1/39095e96302fa4a3ec79a21be70f48cc2e81264f2ac558b4ee3b1eee69401bb9/https%3A//download.mozilla.org/%3Fproduct=thunderbird-24.2.0&amp;amp;os=osx&amp;amp;lang=en-US"&gt;Thunderbird&lt;/a&gt;

&lt;a rel="nofollow" href="http://outgoing.mozilla.org/v1/0ccc94a0a65abe25cd784b751705b07f456f03363e6919bd64b537f8fd320fda/https%3A//download.mozilla.org/%3Fproduct=seamonkey-2.23&amp;amp;os=osx&amp;amp;lang=en-US"&gt;Seamonkey&lt;/a&gt;

Each download item contains below elements:

You can also right click on each download item to get a context menu for more actions and information which are described as below:
&lt;ul&gt;&lt;li&gt;&lt;b&gt;Avaa:&lt;/b&gt; Opens or executes the download file. This option will be available after download has completed.&lt;/li&gt;&lt;li&gt;&lt;b&gt;Näytä tiedosto:&lt;/b&gt; Shows the Download file in its containing folder.&lt;/li&gt;&lt;li&gt;&lt;b&gt;Näytä lataukset:&lt;/b&gt; Shows the Download History window.&lt;/li&gt;&lt;li&gt;&lt;b&gt;Virusskannaus:&lt;/b&gt; Scans the download file manually with the Security Software you assigned. This option will ask you to locate and assign a Security Software if you did not assign already.&lt;/li&gt;&lt;li&gt;&lt;b&gt;Tarkistussumma:&lt;/b&gt; Opens up Checksum window where you can calculate and compare MD5, MD2, SHA1, SHA256, SHA384, SHA512 values for the downloaded file.&lt;/li&gt;&lt;li&gt;&lt;b&gt;Nimeä uudelleen:&lt;/b&gt; Opens up Rename window to let you rename your downloaded file. This option will be available after download has completed.&lt;/li&gt;&lt;li&gt;&lt;b&gt;Poista tiedosto:&lt;/b&gt; Deletes downloaded file from your computer. It will ask you confirmation before attempting to delete the file. This option will be available after download has completed.&lt;/li&gt;&lt;li&gt;&lt;b&gt;Mene lataussivulle:&lt;/b&gt; Opens up download page in a new tab.&lt;/li&gt;&lt;li&gt;&lt;b&gt;Kopioi latauslinkki:&lt;/b&gt; Copies download URL to the Clipboard.&lt;/li&gt;&lt;li&gt;&lt;b&gt;Peruuta:&lt;/b&gt; Cancels the active download and removes the download file from your computer. This option is available for the downloads that are in progress.&lt;/li&gt;&lt;li&gt;&lt;b&gt;Tauko:&lt;/b&gt; Pauses the active download.&lt;/li&gt;&lt;li&gt;&lt;b&gt;Jatka:&lt;/b&gt; Resumes the paused download.&lt;/li&gt;&lt;li&gt;&lt;b&gt;Tyhjennä:&lt;/b&gt; Clears the download item from Download Bar.&lt;/li&gt;&lt;/ul&gt;You can also left click on each download item to open up Information Popup for the related download which is described below in detail:
&lt;ul&gt;&lt;li&gt;&lt;b&gt;Lähde:&lt;/b&gt; Source URL of the download file. Left clicking on Source link will open up Source URL in browser as a new tab. Right clicking on Source link opens Copy menu to copy the Source URL of the download.&lt;/li&gt;&lt;li&gt;&lt;b&gt;Kohde:&lt;/b&gt; Location at which the downloaded file is stored on your computer. Left clicking on Target link will open up the download file in its containing folder. Right clicking on Target link opens Copy menu to copy the file path of the download file.&lt;/li&gt;&lt;li&gt;&lt;b&gt;Nykyinen nopeus:&lt;/b&gt; Current download speed of the active download in KB/s.&lt;/li&gt;&lt;li&gt;&lt;b&gt;Keskinopeus:&lt;/b&gt; Average download speed of the completed download in KB/s. This information will be available after download has completed.&lt;/li&gt;&lt;li&gt;&lt;b&gt;Edistyminen:&lt;/b&gt; Progress percent completed for the download.&lt;/li&gt;&lt;li&gt;&lt;b&gt;Jäljellä oleva aika:&lt;/b&gt; Remaining time to complete the download.&lt;/li&gt;&lt;li&gt;&lt;b&gt;Latausaika:&lt;/b&gt; Time spent to complete the download. This information will be available after download has completed.&lt;/li&gt;&lt;li&gt;&lt;b&gt;Ladattu:&lt;/b&gt; First section of this field indicates Current Bytes which is the number of bytes currently transferred while the second section indicates Total Bytes which is the total number of bytes to be transferred before the download finishes.&lt;/li&gt;&lt;li&gt;&lt;b&gt;Tiedostokoko:&lt;/b&gt; Size of the download file on disk. This information will be available after download has completed.&lt;/li&gt;&lt;li&gt;&lt;b&gt;MD5-tarkistussumma:&lt;/b&gt; Automatically calculated MD5 Hash of the downloaded file. This information will be available after download has completed.&lt;/li&gt;&lt;/ul&gt;Information Popup also contains Preview feature for downloaded images to preview them as thumbnails. Preview feature supports PNG, JPG, GIF and BMP file types. Clicking on Preview thumbnail opens the dowmloaded image in the browser as a new tab.

You can also hover over a download item to open up Information Tooltip to get download details in a quick pace.

&lt;b&gt;Tip:&lt;/b&gt; Double clicking on download item will automatically Launch downloaded file.

&lt;b&gt;Tip:&lt;/b&gt; Double clicking on Download Bar automatically clears all completed downloads.

&lt;b&gt;Tip:&lt;/b&gt; Middle clicking on download item will clear it from Download Bar.

&lt;b&gt;Tip:&lt;/b&gt; Left clicking on empty space in Download Bar will open up Add-on Context Menu.

You can customise Download Status Bar according to your needs by the Options window. You can open up Options window by right clicking on Downloads button and selecting Options menu. As an alternative, you can click Tools from Firefox menu, then go to Add-ons, find Download Status Bar in the Extensions tab and click on Preferences button to open up Options window. Available options are described as below:
&lt;ul&gt;&lt;li&gt;&lt;b&gt;Tyhjennä lataus avaamisen jälkeen:&lt;/b&gt; Checking this option will let you clear download item automatically from Download bar after you Launch the file either by context menu Launch option or simply double clicking on Download item.&lt;/li&gt;&lt;li&gt;&lt;b&gt;Tyhjennä lataus tiedoston näyttämisen jälkeen:&lt;/b&gt; Checking this option will let you clear download item automatically from Download bar after showing the download file in its containing folder.&lt;/li&gt;&lt;li&gt;&lt;b&gt;Avaa latauskansio automaattisesti kun lataus on valmis:&lt;/b&gt; Checking this option will let you open up Download directory automatically after the download completes.&lt;/li&gt;&lt;li&gt;&lt;b&gt;Avaa Lataukset-välilehti automaattisesti kun lataus alkaa:&lt;/b&gt; Checking this option will let you open up Download Tab automatically in the browser as a tab when a download starts.&lt;/li&gt;&lt;li&gt;&lt;b&gt;Tyhjennä valmiit lataukset kun Firefox suljetaan:&lt;/b&gt; Download Status Bar keeps the History of your downloads from previous session and shows them up in the Download Bar again when the new session starts. If you do not want to keep download History in Download Bar, you can check this option to clear Download items automatically from History when Firefox quits.&lt;/li&gt;&lt;li&gt;&lt;b&gt;Kysy varmistus ennen tiedoston poistoa:&lt;/b&gt; Before deleting a download item, Download Status Bar ask confirmation to prevent unintended delete actions. If you do not want this confirmation window to speed up the delete process, you can uncheck this option.&lt;/li&gt;&lt;li&gt;&lt;b&gt;Sulje palkki automaattisesti kun kaikki lataukset ovat valmiit:&lt;/b&gt; Checking this option will let you keep Download Bar when there are active Downloads but hide it automatically when all Downloads complete to preserve the web page area. You can also specify a time interval before the Download Bar automatically disappears. &lt;/li&gt;&lt;li&gt;&lt;b&gt;Tyhjennä seuraavat tiedostotyypit automaattisesti:&lt;/b&gt; You may find some file types unimportant to keep in Download Bar and want to clear them automatically after a specific time interval. You can type the file extensions to clear in this field separated by commas. Having an * character in this field is meant to be a short-cut for all file types.&lt;/li&gt;&lt;/ul&gt;&lt;b&gt;Virusskanneri&lt;/b&gt;

You can automatically scan downloaded files by tuning the fields in this options group.
&lt;ul&gt;&lt;li&gt;&lt;b&gt;Virusskannerin polku:&lt;/b&gt; Location at which your preferred Security Software is stored on your computer. Click Locate to open up File Picker to assign a Security Software for Virus Scan if you did not assign already.&lt;/li&gt;&lt;li&gt;&lt;b&gt;Älä skannaa näitä tiedostotyyppejä:&lt;/b&gt; If you want to omit Automatic Virus Scanning for certain file types, you can type their file extensions in this field by comma separated.&lt;/li&gt;&lt;li&gt;&lt;b&gt;Parametrit:&lt;/b&gt; Most of the Security Software does not need any additional arguments for Virus Scan so you can leave this section empty as default. If your Security Software needs additional arguments you can type in this field. You can use %1 expression as a placeholder for the file location of downloaded file.&lt;/li&gt;&lt;li&gt;&lt;b&gt;Skannaa ladatut tiedostot automaattisesti:&lt;/b&gt; Check this option to automatically scan downloaded files by your Security Software when the download completes.&lt;/li&gt;&lt;/ul&gt;&lt;b&gt;Huomautus&lt;/b&gt;

You can get sound notifications when downloads finish by tuning the fields in this options group.
&lt;ul&gt;&lt;li&gt;&lt;b&gt;Äänitiedoston polku:&lt;/b&gt; Location at which your preferred Notification Sound is stored on your computer. Click Locate to open up File Picker to assign a Sound file for Notification if you did not assign already. Possible sound files that can be assigned as notification are .ogg, .wav and .mp3 file types. Default Sound is the notification sound which is included inside the Download Status Bar add-on.&lt;/li&gt;&lt;li&gt;&lt;b&gt;Esikuuntele ääni:&lt;/b&gt; If you want to listen to current Notification Sound, you can click play button of sound player to preview the assigned sound file.&lt;/li&gt;&lt;li&gt;&lt;b&gt;Soita huomautusääni kun lataus on valmis:&lt;/b&gt; Check this option if you want to get sound notifications when downloads are completed.&lt;/li&gt;&lt;li&gt;&lt;b&gt;Nollaa asetukset:&lt;/b&gt; Clicking Reset Settings button will reset the values for Notification options.&lt;/li&gt;&lt;/ul&gt;&lt;b&gt;Ulkoasu&lt;/b&gt;

You can customise the interface of Download Status Bar by the options provided in this tab.

&lt;b&gt;Väri&lt;/b&gt;

You can change the appearance of Download Items by tuning the color pickers in this options group. Each color is gradient based to create a nice effect for the interface elements. Every color change is applied instantly by Download Status Bar:
&lt;ul&gt;&lt;li&gt;&lt;b&gt;Latauksen taustaväri:&lt;/b&gt; Pick a special color from the related Color Picker to assign color for the background of Download Item. Because Progress color will superpose the background color of Download Item when the download finish, you may want to change this color when you start downloading a large file to be able to see how the color looks like.&lt;/li&gt;&lt;li&gt;&lt;b&gt;Latauksen etenemisen väri:&lt;/b&gt; Pick a special color from the related Color Picker to assign it as progress color for the active Downloads. &lt;/li&gt;&lt;li&gt;&lt;b&gt;Latauksen tekstin väri:&lt;/b&gt; Pick a special color from the related Color Picker to assign it as text color for File Name and Progress Section of Download Item.&lt;/li&gt;&lt;li&gt;&lt;b&gt;Valmiin latauksen väri:&lt;/b&gt; Pick a special color from the related Color Picker to assign it as a color to indicate completed Downloads.&lt;/li&gt;&lt;li&gt;&lt;b&gt;Tauotetun latauksen väri:&lt;/b&gt; Pick a special color from the related Color Picker to assign it as a pause color to indicate paused Downloads.&lt;/li&gt;&lt;li&gt;&lt;b&gt;Palkin taustaväri:&lt;/b&gt; Pick a special color from the related Color Picker to assign it as a background color for Download Bar.&lt;/li&gt;&lt;li&gt;&lt;b&gt;Nollaa asetukset:&lt;/b&gt; Clicking Reset Settings button will reset the values for Color options.&lt;/li&gt;&lt;/ul&gt;&lt;b&gt;Latausnopeus&lt;/b&gt;

You can assign different colors for different download speeds by tuning the fields in this options group. Assigning Speed Colors will overwrite the Progress Color from the Color options group if you assigned any.

&lt;b&gt;Käyttöliittymä&lt;/b&gt;

You can change the interface of Download Status Bar by the fields provided in this options group:
&lt;ul&gt;&lt;li&gt;&lt;b&gt;Latauspalkki:&lt;/b&gt; This is the default download interface for Download Status Bar. If you select this option, Download Items are put in the Download Bar which is placed at the bottom section of the browser.&lt;/li&gt;&lt;li&gt;&lt;b&gt;Latauspaneeli:&lt;/b&gt; If you want to keep your Download privacy from others, you can select this option to place all Download Items in a Toolbar Button Panel. The Toolbar Button will be placed in Add-on Bar as default. If there are no Add-on Bar or if Add-on Bar is hidden at the moment, the Toolbar Button will be placed inside the Navigation Toolbar of Firefox. Toolbar Button has also a counter next to it. First section of counter indicates the number of active downloads in progress and the second part of the counter indicates the number of completed downloads.&lt;/li&gt;&lt;/ul&gt;&lt;b&gt;Etenemisen ilmoitukset&lt;/b&gt;

You can hide or show Progress Percent, Speed and Remaining Time items in the Progress Section of Download Items by tuning the checkboxes in this option group.

&lt;b&gt;Etenemisen kohdistaminen&lt;/b&gt;

You can adjust the Progress Section alignment of Download Items by tuning the fields of this options group. Selecting Horizontal option will place Progress, Speed and Remaining Time elements side by side while switching to Vertical place all Progress elements in vertical position.

&lt;b&gt;Ladattava tiedosto&lt;/b&gt;

You can change the width and height values of a Download item  by tuning the fields in this options group:
&lt;ul&gt;&lt;li&gt;&lt;b&gt;Leveys:&lt;/b&gt; Place a numerical value in this field to set the width of the Download Item.&lt;/li&gt;&lt;li&gt;&lt;b&gt;Korkeus:&lt;/b&gt; Place a numerical value in this field to set the height of the Download Item.&lt;/li&gt;&lt;li&gt;&lt;b&gt;Tiedostonimen fonttikoko:&lt;/b&gt; Place a numerical value in this field to set the font size for the File Name of the Download Item.&lt;/li&gt;&lt;li&gt;&lt;b&gt;Etenemisen fonttikoko:&lt;/b&gt; Place a numerical value in this field to set the font size for the Progress Section of the Download Item.&lt;/li&gt;&lt;/ul&gt;&lt;b&gt;Piilota Tyhjennä-nappi latauspalkissa:&lt;/b&gt; Checking this option will hide Clear button in Download Bar.

&lt;b&gt;Piilota Lataukset-nappi latauspalkissa:&lt;/b&gt; Checking this option will hide Download button in Download Bar.

Tämä sivu on saatavana myös seuraavilla kielillä:

