&lt;i&gt;&lt;b&gt;Features &amp;amp; Options for Thunderbird&lt;/b&gt;&lt;/i&gt;

&lt;ul&gt;&lt;li&gt;&lt;b&gt;classic toolbar buttons style for ...&lt;/b&gt;&lt;ul&gt;&lt;li&gt;... toolbar buttons on tabs toolbar&lt;/li&gt;&lt;li&gt;... toolbar buttons on menu toolbar&lt;/li&gt;&lt;li&gt;... toolbar buttons on main toolbars&lt;/li&gt;&lt;/ul&gt;&lt;/li&gt;&lt;li&gt;&lt;b&gt; toolbar button icon settings&lt;/b&gt;&lt;ul&gt;&lt;li&gt;default (let Thunderbird or a theme or a third party add-on decide)&lt;/li&gt;&lt;li&gt;Thunderbird (dark)&lt;/li&gt;&lt;li&gt;Thunderbird (white)&lt;/li&gt;&lt;li&gt;Thunderbird 1&lt;/li&gt;&lt;li&gt;Thunderbird 2&lt;/li&gt;&lt;li&gt;Thunderbird 3&lt;/li&gt;&lt;li&gt;Thunderbird 3 (Strata)&lt;/li&gt;&lt;li&gt;Thunderbird (MacOSX)&lt;/li&gt;&lt;/ul&gt;&lt;/li&gt;&lt;li&gt;&lt;b&gt;toolbar button dropmarker icon settings&lt;/b&gt;&lt;ul&gt;&lt;li&gt;default (let Thunderbird or a third party add-on decide)&lt;/li&gt;&lt;li&gt;dark &amp;amp; small icon&lt;/li&gt;&lt;li&gt;dark &amp;amp; big icon&lt;/li&gt;&lt;li&gt;white &amp;amp; small icon&lt;/li&gt;&lt;li&gt;white &amp;amp; big icon&lt;/li&gt;&lt;/ul&gt;&lt;/li&gt;&lt;li&gt;&lt;b&gt;change toolbar buttons border radius&lt;/b&gt;&lt;/li&gt;&lt;li&gt;&lt;b&gt;change toolbar buttons height/width&lt;/b&gt;&lt;/li&gt;&lt;li&gt;&lt;b&gt;change spaces around and between toolbar buttons&lt;/b&gt;&lt;/li&gt;&lt;/ul&gt;
&lt;i&gt;&lt;b&gt;Features &amp;amp; Options for Seamonkey&lt;/b&gt;&lt;/i&gt;

&lt;ul&gt;&lt;li&gt;&lt;b&gt;classic toolbar buttons style for ...&lt;/b&gt;&lt;ul&gt;&lt;li&gt;... toolbar buttons on menu toolbar&lt;/li&gt;&lt;li&gt;... toolbar buttons on main toolbars (browser, mail, composer, adressbook, editor, Lightning)&lt;/li&gt;&lt;li&gt;... toolbar buttons on bookmarks toolbar&lt;/li&gt;&lt;li&gt;... items and folders on bookmarks toolbar&lt;/li&gt;&lt;/ul&gt;&lt;/li&gt;&lt;li&gt;&lt;b&gt; toolbar button icon settings&lt;/b&gt;&lt;ul&gt;&lt;li&gt;default (let Seamonkey or a theme or a third party add-on decide)&lt;/li&gt;&lt;li&gt;Firefox 1&lt;/li&gt;&lt;li&gt;Firefox 2&lt;/li&gt;&lt;li&gt;Firefox 3&lt;/li&gt;&lt;li&gt;Firefox 3 (Strata)&lt;/li&gt;&lt;li&gt;Firefox 4-12 (dark)&lt;/li&gt;&lt;li&gt;Firefox 4-12 (white)&lt;/li&gt;&lt;li&gt;Firefox 13+ (dark)&lt;/li&gt;&lt;li&gt;Firefox 13+ (white)&lt;/li&gt;&lt;li&gt;Firefox Ubuntu (thx to &lt;a rel="nofollow" href="https://addons.mozilla.org/user/1908040/"&gt;Bollerkopp&lt;/a&gt; &amp;amp; &lt;a rel="nofollow" href="http://outgoing.mozilla.org/v1/42429e7854652071ff85875781edc6bc85f9d328dfeed5e9c9e7cb3bedc9bcd4/http%3A//tango.freedesktop.org/Tango_Desktop_Project"&gt;Tango Desktop Project&lt;/a&gt;)&lt;/li&gt;&lt;li&gt;Firefox MacOSX&lt;/li&gt;&lt;li&gt;Firefox (Mozilla mix)&lt;/li&gt;&lt;li&gt;Noia&lt;/li&gt;&lt;/ul&gt;&lt;/li&gt;&lt;li&gt;&lt;b&gt; toolbar button icon settings&lt;/b&gt;&lt;ul&gt;&lt;li&gt;default (let Seamonkey or a theme or a third party add-on decide)&lt;/li&gt;&lt;li&gt;Thunderbird (dark)&lt;/li&gt;&lt;li&gt;Thunderbird (white)&lt;/li&gt;&lt;li&gt;Thunderbird 1&lt;/li&gt;&lt;li&gt;Thunderbird 2&lt;/li&gt;&lt;li&gt;Thunderbird 3&lt;/li&gt;&lt;li&gt;Thunderbird 3 (Strata)&lt;/li&gt;&lt;li&gt;Thunderbird (MacOSX)&lt;/li&gt;&lt;/ul&gt;&lt;/li&gt;&lt;li&gt;&lt;b&gt;toolbar button dropmarker icon settings&lt;/b&gt;&lt;ul&gt;&lt;li&gt;default (let Seamonkey or a third party add-on decide)&lt;/li&gt;&lt;li&gt;dark &amp;amp; small icon&lt;/li&gt;&lt;li&gt;dark &amp;amp; big icon&lt;/li&gt;&lt;li&gt;white &amp;amp; small icon&lt;/li&gt;&lt;li&gt;white &amp;amp; big icon&lt;/li&gt;&lt;/ul&gt;&lt;/li&gt;&lt;li&gt;&lt;b&gt;change toolbar buttons border radius&lt;/b&gt;&lt;/li&gt;&lt;li&gt;&lt;b&gt;change toolbar buttons height/width&lt;/b&gt;&lt;/li&gt;&lt;li&gt;&lt;b&gt;change spaces around and between toolbar buttons&lt;/b&gt;&lt;/li&gt;&lt;/ul&gt;
&lt;b&gt;Notes&lt;/b&gt;
All settings are for the default theme, but they "may" work with other themes and toolbar-styling add-ons too, like L.A.R Grizzlys themes, Statini Super theme, Strata M4 theme, Tangerinefox theme and maybe others!

&lt;b&gt;Firefox / Thunderbird / Seamonkey&lt;/b&gt;
&lt;ul&gt;&lt;li&gt;Firefox settings are only visible on Firefox&lt;/li&gt;&lt;li&gt;Thunderbird settings are only visible on Thunderbird&lt;/li&gt;&lt;li&gt;Seamonkey settings are only visible on Seamonkey&lt;/li&gt;&lt;/ul&gt;
&lt;b&gt;"Add-on Compatibility Reporter" add-on&lt;/b&gt;
If you have problems or find bugs, please contact me by email (provided inside my profile) or use this add-ons support page. Sending (false) reports using "Add-on compatibility Reporter"-extension without a proper description are &lt;b&gt;not valid&lt;/b&gt; and cannot be fixed!</description><dc:creator xmlns:dc="http://purl.org/dc/elements/1.1/">Aris</dc:creator><pubDate>Sat, 21 Jun 2014 08:54:45 -0700</pubDate><guid>https://addons.mozilla.org/fI/thunderbird/addon/cstbb/versions/1.4.1</guid></item><item><title>EHTip 2.4.4</title><link>https://addons.mozilla.org/fI/thunderbird/addon/ehtip/</link><description>Main features:

- Uses local integrated dictionaries for fast (instant) translations.
- Translates words hovered by mouse.
- Translates selected words.
- Replaces translated words choosing one from its translation.
- Ability to add user dictionaries (English⟷German, English⟷Hungarian, English⟷Czech on home page).

-- Hrvatski --

Englesko-Hrvatski i Hrvatsko-Engleski rječnik za Firefox.

Glavna obilježja:
- Koristi lokalne integrirane rječnike za brzo (neposredno) prevođenje.
- Prevodi riječi pod pokazivačem miša.
- Prevodi označene riječi.
- Izmjenjuje prevedenu riječ odabirom jedne iz njenog prijevoda.
- Mogućnost dodavanja korisničkih rječnika (Engleski⟷Njemački, Engleski⟷Mađarski, Engleski⟷Češki na stranici projekta).</description><dc:creator xmlns:dc="http://purl.org/dc/elements/1.1/">Robert Katić</dc:creator><pubDate>Wed, 19 Sep 2012 21:19:30 -0700</pubDate><guid>https://addons.mozilla.org/fI/thunderbird/addon/ehtip/versions/2.4.4</guid></item><item><title>QuickFolders (Tabbed Folders) 3.14.1</title><link>https://addons.mozilla.org/fI/thunderbird/addon/quickfolders-tabbed-folders/</link><description>Bookmark mail folders in Thunderbird. 

This extension adds an extra toolbar to Thunderbird. When you drag a mail folder to it, you get a fully customizable shortcut to that mail folder. This supports full drag and drop, like the corresponding folder in the folder tree - You can drag messages on it to move/copy them to the folder, and access the bookmarked folders through keyboard shortcuts.

This is handy when you have a large tree of folders for clients or projects, but use only a few of them at the same time.

The Category feature adds more usability by adding distinct areas to work in; this can make it easier to focus on a task that needs just a subset of the folders visible. There is also excellent integration with the Thunderbird tabbed interface provided since Tb version 3.</description><dc:creator xmlns:dc="http://purl.org/dc/elements/1.1/">Realraven (Axel Grude)</dc:creator><pubDate>Fri, 14 Feb 2014 09:37:02 -0800</pubDate><guid>https://addons.mozilla.org/fI/thunderbird/addon/quickfolders-tabbed-folders/versions/3.14.1</guid></item><item><title>Copy Plain Text 2 1.3.1</title><link>https://addons.mozilla.org/fI/thunderbird/addon/copy-plain-text-2/</link><description>With this addon you can copy selected text without any formatting such as italic, bold, font size, etc. Just select text, right click and from context menu choose "Copy as plain text". Addon is customizable, so from options dialog you can choose some copy options. In the Copy Plain Text 2 feature "Make as default COPY action" not require application restart. Specially designed for AutoCopy2.
